{"tid":1704264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又一城深夜疑點整合","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:39:37.000Z","uid":249040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4e7258ac0d7db0bb398910f7e720cc5ec89862","tid":1704264,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1） 下午事發幾個鐘之後，夜晚10點幾無端端call兩架白車到又一城<br />\n<br />\n2） 封左商場單獨黎講，都未必成疑， 但集合埋其他蘋果live見到（23:15）：<br />\n<br />\n3） 幾個便衣蒙面popo呢個鐘數，仲係商場度行黎行去（已對蘋果承認係狗） ，原因可能係睇場/蒐證/扮手足<br />\n<br />\n4） 地下好大灘血漿，認得係溜冰場對出 前少少個位（反戲院方向），連埋地上好多紙巾雜物，下午到宜家咁多個鐘，都無人清過，一定係異常重大事情要留證據/改證據 先唔比人掂，普通死傷唔會咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xq9F4LD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxq9F4LD.png&h=d56375cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f111740103f7ffa12b4cce688f8622e50c3086b3","tid":1704264,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6ad74147062e8538bd51e842dd740cd67cb0799","tid":1704264,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"大家集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708d09795f4ef8f9e47a7598a7b219a155814ced","tid":1704264,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"我要真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2b31f8d2d9e18560d5715fa63e19107b9d9d06","tid":1704264,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8778bc881be40bc6fd2b1287df9219230f666a3","tid":1704264,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"6259e64